Description:
Renovated Corryong Cottage
This lovely cottage lifts renovation to a new high. The cottage has been rebuilt from the stumps up. It includes 3 bedrooms, featuring high ceiling and timber floors. Timber floors flow through the entry, lounge, dining and continues on rear sun filled deck.
The light filled living area to the rear of the property includes kitchen with windows to an outdoor entertaining area, renovated bathroom and large open meals area, with air conditioning and slow combustion log fire for those cold winter nights. The cottage garden is welcoming and thoughtfully landscaped combining old and new plants. The private deck is perfect for coffee and to sit and enjoy the outdoors. Inspect by appointment

Description:
Majestic 24SQ home on 3.1 hectares overlooking district
5 year old weatherboard home based on typical Australian rural style with views to thrill. The open plan living home with 4 bedrooms, plus study, opens to wide all round verandahs. The extra wide hallway allows those summer breezes to help maintain great air flow through the home.
Quality inclusions, solar hot water, ceiling fans, reverse cycle split system unit, combustion heater and dream kitchen will "knock your socks off".
The landscaped surrounds and established gardens finish off the property.
Just move in, enjoy the country living at Corryong and take in the beautiful Upper Murray. You will not be disappointed.
Inspection by appointment only with Reg Coulston 0418 118 207 or David Gittoes 0409 362 722

Description:
CORNER THE MARKET
"The Convent” was built in the 1960’s and is in immaculate condition with Murray Pine floors, timber door and window frames and solid timber doors. Located in an ideal location with three street frontages the position and potential is a one off.
The dwelling comprises six (6) principle bedrooms, three (3) with hand basins and five (5) with built in robes.
The original kitchen offers an adjoining, large, walk-in pantry, an abundance of cupboards plus a slow combustion cooker and an electric cooker.
Central large dining/lounge area with electric heater, split system and storage room. A second large lounge/retreat has built-in bookcases and cupboards.
The bathroom/wet area wing features a bathroom with bath, shower, a separate toilet and a shower room.
Evaporative air conditioning unit cools the dwelling.
There is ample storage. The dwelling has a rear entertainment area, a low maintenance garden surrounded with Colorbond fencing. Shedding comprises single carport and a lock-up shed.
Situated in Corryong Township on two (2) titles of ½ acre each (2000m2) combined being (4000m2).

Description:
Finest Single Level Living in the Upper Murray
In arguably Corryongs best streets, with the golf course, air port and township a short stroll away, this exquisite contemporary home enjoys its prime viewing position of Mt Mittamattite
Deceptive spacious on large allotment in this sought after location, the single-level design allows seamless living throughout with a generous floor-plan, offering exceptional four bedroom accommodation. Stunning living areas overlook the mountain and open directly to the sun filled entertaining & BBQ area.
An impressive gourmet kitchen is fully equipped easily catering for large scale entertaining. The fireplace creates the perfect feature as the sun sets, while the high ceilings and uninterrupted views out to the valley and mountain provide the ultimate daytime panorama.
Air-conditioned & hydronic heated throughout with a list of features to numerous too mention: Inspection is highly recommended

Description:
Quality Refurbished Three bedroom House
Sited on a elevated block, this well presented home has been recently updated, giving a fabulous blend of traditional features and modern, light-filled living zones. The home consists of three bedrooms, one bathroom, open plan living and kitchen with polished hardwood floors, new cabinetry, quality appliances. There is a separate dining space, laundry. Heating and cooling is by an efficient rev-cycle air-conditioner.
The large deck, accessed through large glass doors from the living area, with rear deck area ideal for al-fresco dining.
Located within easy walk to all facilities, in a quiet street the home suits as a family home or investor property.
An inspection highly reccomended

Description:
Own your slice of Man from Snowy River Country?
After generations, the time has come to offer this magnificent property to the market.
With an abundance of permanent water; a large dam and natural waterway run through this 36.42 hectares (90 acre), Man from Snowy River property.
Ideally located just 18 kms from Corryong, and 130 kms from Albury Wodonga. The property has generous paddocks, undulating land, good yards, and shedding.
Complete with a well-designed and beautifully presented low maintenance new home with superb views of the valley.
This is a once in a lifetime opportunity!

Description:
UPPER MURRAY LIFESTYLE INVESTMENT - 2.03 Hectares - 5.01 Acres
ALL OFFERS CONSIDERED.
Fabulous investment property with modern brick family home with huge outdoor entertaining, verandah all the way around, four bedrooms with built-in robes, large master bedroom with ensuite and walk-in robe, open plan living and tasteful Tasmanian oak kitchen.
Sheds outside, fruit trees, loading ramp for stock and plenty of room for all those country pursuits.
If you want a comfortable future in Corryong this is it. Inspections recommended.
